%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NoB2Z8q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/joncoopertweets/status/1498053625813286929</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qHxiMbt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[springelmogizmo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Lessons learned</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/T0OhBCK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RMBwiQq.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://twitter.com/NoLieWithBTC/status/1498069869568282624

https://www.newyorker.com/news/annals-of-inquiry/the-ukraine-transparency-initiative</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/T0OhBCK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[somemonkey]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>For Educational Purposes Only</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GNRDxuc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HILDICA.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Don't try this at home</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gAIXw6f.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Don't put these on roads</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PnClUkY.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This would ruin someone's tire</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gOsIiYz.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nails and a hose pipe should not be used like this</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gyvsofj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Be careful with old bit of wood with nails and screws sticking out</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/d5hzKW2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nails in your hosepipe makes holes in tubes</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bSNtT9L.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hollow spikes let the air out faster than solid spikes. Don't drive over them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4VLDNk1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dirty tubes are hard to see on roads, be careful how you dispose of them</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wLqfK4d.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Screws in wooden strips or plywood are potentially dangerous, don't paint them in dark colours.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iEowcVm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Light coloured wood with screws in is easily seen.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fENY1DR.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Waste from building sites might have screws and nails in them, don't leave them laying around where they could damage other people's vehicles.

The above images are for educational purposes only and offer advice on safety issues surrounding household and workshop items.

Stay safe Ukraine.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GNRDxuc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MaxximumB]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Created this portrait of President Zelenskyy to show my support! Slava Ukraini!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RDurE1b</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/w8gTdhu.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RDurE1b</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Joyousjoyfuljoyness]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is important, please read: Disinformation Campaigns</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0uHGNiW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Z4kqcfV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iqnHjlW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7i9EBZe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3K3qkip.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hqb7LvW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YuU1hSb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/viyrO23.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f53lAYl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5KpcJPS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/42kTObd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UPpTLMF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jZ3opjL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PZgX1Kn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L5s8rYT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fCYVfkB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VX61A5u.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9cOZsje.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Xyt9Lio.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GsS84SS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0ewjOoj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You will read a lot of content, it's important to view it all with a critical eye. 

This includes solicitations for money, downloading an app to challenge "misinformation," posts meant to enrage that are from entirely different places outside of Ukraine.

Use common sense. Donate to established charities like the Red Cross, fact check something that looks odd, trust reliable sources.

What is happening in Ukraine is heartbreaking and our gut reaction is to want to help, to do something.

But as the reporter above noted, this has been going on a very long time, and social engineering has become incredibly more sophisticated.

Stay safe, be smart. And let's hope this gets resolved before some asshat pushes a button.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0uHGNiW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[displacedgothamist]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Would not recommend</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vPqE52l</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JiKdO0V.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vPqE52l</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[codrcrew]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Heartwarming or scary?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LXZG0IN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wimTkTN.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LXZG0IN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThatOtherGirlYouKnow]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Just stop talking about him. You’re giving him power.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4qqXkWC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/62mJ7Rm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Viral edit: Look, Trump may be relevant in the future. But right now, his claims and statements are unverifiable ego-stroking trash. He isn’t in power now, so his opinions and statements don’t matter, especially when we’re talking about Ukraine, a situation he helped to cause. Let’s not humour him with any recognition.

