I don't know what to do. I feel bad and her too.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/eg2S8T6</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[papymomo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Georgian ship refused to give fuel to a russian ship (eng. subtitles)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zllqWZ1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lj4cv1Q.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zllqWZ1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Xiph0IdJANKY836]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Salute to Ukraine!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DhdfzhD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LmK3kLg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Solidarity to all the Ukrainians courageously defending against a cruel and evil invasion. The world is with you!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DhdfzhD</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[bivalve]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Last Call for AlcoHAUL THEM AWAY</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kzqUzIr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xxV8Orp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Link to tweet:

